"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-world-paris-olympics-la-defense-arena-sustainability-b1160587.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News|World  Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena is not your typicalOlympicand Paralympic swimming venue.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For one thing, there is currently no water.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, until recently, the area where the pool must go was plastered with dozens of trucks and sparkly sequins, dismantling the set ofTaylor Swift's Eras Tour, whose European leg kicked off in Parisearlier this month.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Gehrels_Swift_Observatory\", \"score\": 0.6650400132345805, \"rank\": 0.5034436515064102, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q2133344\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Gehrels_Swift_Observatory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Gehrels_Swift_Observatory\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet within hours, both the hardware and glitter had gone.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to its modular and multi-purpose structure, the arena - which first opened its doors in 2017 and was designed by architect Christian de Portzamparc - will soon be host to an Olympic-sized swimming pool and warm-up areas, as if Taylor (or the rugby pitch belonging to Racing 92, its resident club) never existed.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is difficult to describe the arena's scale but let me try.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is Europe's largest indoor venue, capable of hosting up to 45,000 people.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is home to the world's largest interactive giant screen, with 1,400 square metres worth of display area, equivalent to seven tennis courts.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Its roof can handle 250 tonnes of weight.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The history of theOlympic Gameshas all too often been one of cost overruns and white elephants.Paris 2024wants to change all that - an impressive 95 per cent of its Olympic venues are existing or temporary, which is vital for an event with sustainability at its heart.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this way, Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena is a worthy venue which has incorporated energy efficiency and sustainability into its development from the very beginning.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_La_D\\u00e9fense_Arena\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than traditional (and energy-intensive) heating and air conditioning systems, the facility relies upon high-performance thermal and acoustic insulation, which can ensure uniform temperatures regardless of outdoor weather conditions.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, any collected rainwater funnels into an 800m\\u00b3 storage tank located beneath the underground car park.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This water provides 100 per cent of the lawn irrigation needs.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, solar panels on the roof are used to power the adjoining brewery.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The arena's waste management policy is also impressive.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since May 2022, it has established its own on-site waste sorting centre.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By 2025, it aims for an 80 per cent recycling rate and 40 per cent energy reduction.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it's good enough for Taylor and around 180,000 Swifties, it should work for the Olympics and Paralympics.\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 3419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999817904747887, \"rank\": 1.8136087546709706e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999817904747887, \"rank\": 1.8136087546709706e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 2779, \"end\": 2787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"score\": 0.999999715714734, \"rank\": 2.842839411651421e-07, \"text\": \"Brighton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\"}, {\"begin\": 2845, \"end\": 2859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999777174, \"rank\": 1.9332113747